text.tspan: Weekly confirmed cases of influenza A H1
This shows the number of cases that were confirmed to be of the H1 strain of influenza A virus. Only a fraction
of potential cases of influenza are tested by labs to confirm whether they have influenza and to identify their
strain. The level of testing may vary between countries and over time.
Data source: FluNet by the World Health Organization (2023)
